title: Riley.Greygate
tags:
---
Greygate, hm? 
<<displaypromptmenuask Managers GenAAA>>
Have you ever been there?
<<set $beenToGreygate to react("value", "", "Riley")>>
<<if $beenToGreygate is true>>
    Oh, you have? It's quite the amazing city.
    I go there at least once a year to visit
    my younger brother. He lives near the 
    market terraces, so it's usually a great
    expierience. An expensive one, too, though.
    If you go again you should ride in one of
    the cable cars. They've been installed all
    over town in the recent years.
<<else>>
    You haven't, then? You should definetly go!
    What I can recommend most is going to 
    visit the market terrace. It's a multi-level
    district filled with shops, restaurants,
    auctions and stalls. Like they say you can
    buy everything there - and it's very true.
<<endif>>
[[Riley.Continue]]
