title: Riley.Riley
tags:
---
Me? I'm Riley, Detective from Glomure, 
which is two towns over, if you don't know.
Hm... also I'm 31 years old and I think
this is my fifth year working here.
It's my first murder case, too.
Oh but you wanted to know about me,
not about the case, right?
I grew up in Glomure and still have
family over there. 
People usually expect that I'm married,
but I'm not.
Haven't found the right person yet.
[[Riley.Continue]]
